headline: Why Are CrowdStrike (CRWD) Shares Soaring Today
summary: Shares of cybersecurity platform provider CrowdStrike (NASDAQ:CRWD) jumped 5.3% in the afternoon session after Cantor Fitzgerald reiterated its Overweight rating on the stock, citing the company's accelerating business momentum and improved financial outlook.
